      "extra": {
        "message": "Redis Connection Without TLS\n\nThe Redis connection is established without any TLS/SSL configuration. Session data stored in Redis is transmitted in cleartext over the network.\n\nImpact: An attacker with network access can intercept session data transmitted between the application and Redis.\n\nFix: Configure TLS for the Redis connection by passing SSL parameters to `create_pool()`.",
